      <title class="- topic/title "> 
         <ph class="- topic/ph " props="autonumber">5315.404-1-90</ph> Pricing Assistance or Pricing Assistance Waiver</title>
      <conbody class="- topic/body  concept/conbody ">
         <p outputclass="List1" class="- topic/p ">(a) Required thresholds for requesting pricing
assistance:</p>
         <table class="- topic/table ">
            <tgroup cols="3" class="- topic/tgroup ">
               <colspec colname="col1"
                        colnum="1"
                        colwidth="1.1*"
                        rowheader="headers"
                        class="- topic/colspec "/>
               <colspec colname="col2"
                        colnum="2"
                        colwidth="0.9*"
                        rowheader="headers"
                        class="- topic/colspec "/>
               <colspec colname="col3"
                        colnum="3"
                        colwidth="1*"
                        rowheader="headers"
                        class="- topic/colspec "/>
               <tbody class="- topic/tbody ">
                  <row class="- topic/row ">
                     <entry nameend="col2"
                            namest="col1"
                            class="- topic/entry "
                            align="center"> 
                        <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Sole Source</b> 
                     </entry>
                     <entry class="- topic/entry " align="center"> 
                        <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Competitive</b> 
                     </entry>
                  </row>
                  <row class="- topic/row ">
                     <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                        <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">PEO (Systems)</b>
                     </entry>
                     <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                        <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">All Other</b>
                     </entry>
                     <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                        <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">All</b>
                     </entry>
                  </row>
                  <row class="- topic/row ">
                     <entry class="- topic/entry ">$25M or more</entry>
                     <entry class="- topic/entry ">$10M or more</entry>
                     <entry class="- topic/entry ">$100M or more</entry>
                  </row>
               </tbody>
            </tgroup>
         </table>
         <p outputclass="List1" class="- topic/p ">(b) See <xref format="html"
                  href="https://www.acquisition.gov/daffars/mp5315-contracting-negotiation#DAFFARS_MP5315_404_1_90"
                  scope="external"
                  class="- topic/xref ">MP5315.404-1-90(b)</xref>
for procedures for requesting pricing assistance.</p>
