                  href="https://www.acquisition.gov/daffars/mp5315-contracting-negotiation#DAFFARS_MP5315_404_1_90"
                  scope="external"
                  class="- topic/xref ">MP5315.404-1-90(c)</xref> for procedures for requesting a pricing assistance waiver for actions that meet or exceed the required thresholds identified in <xref outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
